title: Optometry Notes & MCQs
description:
•This app will provide free books for 15-20 subjects of Optometry.
•We will conduct weekly basis 1-3 MCQs test for the students preparing for the Job, Internship, Entrance Exam, and Academic Exam.
•We will provide well organized notes; instead of copy/pasting we provide practical based notes with update information.
•We the Team Smart Optometry are actively working on Youtube, Telegram, Facebook & Blog to spread the knowledge of Optometry.
•Join with us and “Study Optometry Smartly”
